class="section-faq"><div
class="container"><h2 id=fAQs class="section-heading">FAQs:</h2><div
class="row"><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=how-do-i-make-a-modern-and-simple-logo class="question">How do I make a modern and simple logo?</h3><div
class="answer"><ol><li>Consider the products or services your business offers, your target market, and your brand's aesthetic.</li><li>Get inspired by existing logos that are modern and simple.</li><li>Use a <a
href="https://www.notzarla.com/free-logo-maker">logo maker</a> to generate some unique logo design ideas.</li><li>Play around with different icons, fonts, and colors, to create a minimalistic and trendy logo.</li><li>Ask friends and relatives for their honest feedback and adjust your ideas accordingly.</li><li>Choose a memorable logo and download it.</li></ol></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=what-are-modern-and-simple-logos class="question">What are modern and simple logos?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>Modern and simple logos usually have a minimalistic look that's reflected in their icon, font, and color. Icons with simple linework are combined with neat typefaces like Righteous or Federo to create a contemporary feeling. They also typically consist of a trendy color scheme, such as blue and white, or a single shade of brown, black, or red. Take a look at <a
href="#modern-and-simple-logo-ideas">our collection of logo ideas</a> for inspiration.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=which-companies-have-modern-and-simple-logos class="question">Which companies have modern and simple logos?</h3><div
class="answer"><ul><li>Twitter.</li><li>Rolex.</li><li>Nissan.</li><li>Audi.</li><li>Uber.</li><li>Givenchy.</li><li>Chanel.</li><li>Apple.</li><li>Instagram.</li></ul></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=where-can-i-find-some-modern-and-simple-logo-designs class="question">Where can I find some modern and simple logo designs?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>You can go to Zarla's logo maker to create a modern and simple design for your business. Once you've found the perfect option, you can download it for free. To design your logo from a template, simply click on "Edit" beneath one of our examples.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=what-does-a-modern-and-simple-logo-font-look-like class="question">What does a modern and simple logo font look like?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>Fonts that convey feelings of minimalism, trendiness, and elegance work well for a modern and simple logo. If your brand values precision and power, opt for a sizeable, neat font, like Sansation Bold. For a hint of playfulness, use a font with rounded characters, like Averia Serif Libre or Pacifico Regular.</p></div></div><div
class="col-12 faq-item"><h3 id=where-can-i-download-a-modern-and-simple-logo-design-for-free class="question">Where can I download a modern and simple logo design for free?</h3><div
class="answer"><p>Zarla has an AI-powered logo maker that can generate hundreds of unique modern and simple logo designs with just a few clicks. Once you've designed the best logo for your brand, you can download it for free.</p></div></div></div></div></div> <script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How do I make a modern and simple logo?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<ol>\n<li>Consider the products or services your business offers, your target market, and your brand's aesthetic.<\/li>\n<li>Get inspired by existing logos that are modern and simple.<\/li>\n<li>Use a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.zarla.com\/free-logo-maker\">logo maker<\/a> to generate some unique logo design ideas.<\/li>\n<li>Play around with different icons, fonts, and colors, to create a minimalistic and trendy logo.<\/li>\n<li>Ask friends and relatives for their honest feedback and adjust your ideas accordingly.<\/li>\n<li>Choose a memorable logo and download it.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What are modern and simple logos?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<p>Modern and simple logos usually have a minimalistic look that's reflected in their icon, font, and color. Icons with simple linework are combined with neat typefaces like Righteous or Federo to create a contemporary feeling. They also typically consist of a trendy color scheme, such as blue and white, or a single shade of brown, black, or red. Take a look at <a href=\"#modern-and-simple-logo-ideas\">our collection of logo ideas<\/a> for inspiration.<\/p>\n"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which companies have modern and simple logos?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"<ul>\n<li>Twitter.<\/li>\n<li>Rolex.<\/li>\n<li>Nissan.<\/li>\n<li>Audi.<\/li>\n<li>Uber.<\/li>\n<li>Givenchy.<\/li>\n<li>Chanel.<\/li>\n<li>Apple.<\/li>\n<li>Instagram.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Where can I find some modern and